In 2004, Orton appeared on the talk show "Jimmy Kimmel Live!"
to promote Taboo Tuesday.
In March 2007, he appeared alongside Edge, John Cena, and Bobby Lashley on the game show "Deal or No Deal".
In October 2014, Orton became a popular figure on Vine, when a trend began of clips of a superimposed Orton performing his signature RKO move on internet "fail" victims.
